# Get Tails 2.12

- To install, follow our [[installation instructions|install]].

- To upgrade, an automatic upgrade is available from 2.10 and 2.11 to 2.12.

  If you cannot do an automatic upgrade or if you fail to start after an
  automatic upgrade, please try to do a [[manual upgrade|upgrade]].

- [[Download Tails 2.12.|install/download]]

# What's coming up?

Our next release is [[scheduled|contribute/calendar]] for June 13:

- If Debian Stretch is released after June 13, our next release will be 2.13.
- Otherwise, we will try to publish 3.0 before June 13 at the same time as
  Debian Stretch which release schedule has not been announced yet. You can
  already [[test a beta version of Tails 3.0|news/test_3.0-beta3]].

